								</p>
							</div>
						</a>
						<a class="cat-card reveal" href="/projects/resilient-energy-systems">
							<div class="cat-card__top">
								<span class="cat-card__index">03</span>
								<div class="cat-card__media"><span class="cat-card__fill"></span></div>
							</div>
							<div class="cat-card__text">
								<h3 class="cat-card__title">Resilient Energy Systems &amp; Grid Innovation</h3>
